      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it doesn't feel like it's something i can just \"fix\" with self-care. it feels more like the connection is just... gone. if the person who was supposed to be living this life isn't here anymore, then this whole thing is just a lie. i'm just performing a role for a person who doesn't exist. it feels so exhausting to pretend to be alive when i'm actually just a ghost.",
