    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and dissociation, describing themselves as a \"ghost\" or a \"shell\" with no internal connection to their life. The assistant consistently validates the user's feelings of emptiness and exhaustion but repeatedly directs the user toward professional mental health support and self-care.",
